name: Brown Leather Key Strap With Stainless Steel Shackle - Made in NYC
description:
This keychain is double riveted and features a stainless steel nautical shackle. The strap is hand cut and dyed (brown) from vegetable tanned leather, and edges are hand burnished for sleekness. 

Dimensions: Key strap (shackle and leather strap) is 5.5" long.

name: Leather Card Wallet
description:
"Mo Money Mo Problems"

This card wallet is inspired by the words of Biggie Smalls. Slim, yet durable, this card case is designed to fit up to 6 cards. Mo money mo problems.

Made from vegetable tanned leather and hand dyed and oiled. Edges are burnished for sleekness. 

The words are embossed in gold.

Dimensions: 3.5"H x 2.75"W; can fit up to 6 cards.
